[003] Packaging
________________________________________________________________________________

The source to install the software must provide all go modules. Go should
not download the modules. The source providing all go modules is usually:

* syncthing-source-vX.YY.Z.tar.gz

where X.YY.Z is the version. 

The build file use 'go build -mod=vendor'. [0]

